<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/30844201-warren">Warren</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I looked at the Lowe-Porter translation before reading Woods, but was put off by the heavy-handed pseudo-biblical prose in which she rendered it. Wood<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I looked at the Lowe-Porter translation before reading Woods, but was put off by the heavy-handed pseudo-biblical prose in which she rendered it. Woods really makes the book come alive. In his hands it is a joy to read, and I thoroughly recommend switching immediately.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
